Review and investigate data variances or unexpected results, including issue resolution and reconciliation;
Assess, develop, and implement strategies to enhance data quality and ensure data meets Ministry and TOH standards;
Support various projects and working groups, implementation of new data extracts, etc;
Prepare, edit and maintain workflows, processes, procedures and documentation.











